00:27:02.720 --> 00:27:07.270
which is a distinction between
abstract knowledge at the top

00:27:07.270 --> 00:27:09.410
and applied knowledge
at the bottom.

00:27:09.410 --> 00:27:11.480
So that's kind of
the old paradigm.

00:27:11.480 --> 00:27:16.670
And throughout that clip,
